> weird, since you would think the increased
> electrical load of the brake
> lights coming on would make them slow down, not
> speed up. Any thoughts on
> this? I'm thinking they get a better ground when the
> taillight circuit is
> brought into play, so speed up? Just a guess on my
> part. 
